name: INABA Churu Bisque for Cats, Creamy Lickable Purée Side Dish with Vitamin E, 1.4 Ounces per Pouch, 12 Pouches, Tuna & Chicken Variety
short_description: MADE WITH WHOLESOME INGREDIENTS YOU CAN TRUST: Every Inaba product is made with yummy high-quality ingredients including farm-raised chicken and/or natural wild-caught tuna
RICH & CREAMY: Churu Bisque is a rich and creamy purée like our original Churu lickable cat treats, but with a thicker consistency that is perfect to serve as a side dish

TASTY TOPPER: Top their meal with a luscious treat that is healthy and hydrating. Each pouch has 91% moisture and only 16 calories, so you can feel good about adding it to their bowl of bland dry cat food
FREE FROM THE BAD STUFF: Each serving is grain-free, preservative-free, carrageenan-free and free from artificial colors, but we've added Vitamin E for your cat's immunity
CONVENIENT COMPLEMENTS: These convenient individual pouches make a perfect side-dish or complement to your fur babies meal
product_description: Here at Inaba, we know your cat is a beloved family member. That's why our Churu Bisque Lickable Creamy Purée for Cats is made from high-quality ingredients including farm-raised chicken and wild-caught tuna. Each pouch contains a mouthwatering purée bisque that is both healthy and hydrating with 91% moisture and 16 calories per serving. We've also made it grain-free, preservative-free, carrageenan-free and free from artificial colors. We've added Vitamin E to help support your cat's immune system, so these are a treat you can feel good about feeding your cat. Perfect for all ages-kitten to senior, simply tear open the pouch and pour out the delicious thick bisque. Use as a side dish, complement to a meal, wet/dry cat food topper or as a special treat, your kitties will thank you from the bottom of their paws. Inaba makes snack time fun for you and your cat.
